```

---

### Scan HTTPS

```bash id="a3szd0"
nmap -p 443 --script http-enum <target>
```

---

### Increase Coverage (All Ports)

```bash id="zv3q7x"
nmap -p- --script http-enum <target>
```

---

### Combine with Other Scripts

```bash id="d0k3mz"
nmap -p 80 --script http-enum,http-title,http-headers <target>
```

