## 🔍 Interpreting Results

### ✅ Valid Findings

```id="n7h4u9"
/admin/ (200 OK)
```

* Directory exists and accessible

---

### ⚠️ Restricted but Interesting

```id="q5j3lz"
/backup/ (403 Forbidden)
```

* Resource exists but blocked
* Worth further testing

---

### 🔁 Redirected

```id="4p4bxx"
/login → /auth/login
```

* Likely valid endpoint

---

### ❌ Not Found

```id="v1l6jw"
/randomfile (404)
```

* No useful information

